945
01:18:59,203 --> 01:19:01,423
[SPEAKER_03]: I didn't mean to throw him under the bus at all.

946
01:19:01,524 --> 01:19:03,864
[SPEAKER_03]: It was my ignorance about how that actually gets done.

947
01:19:03,945 --> 01:19:13,809
[SPEAKER_03]: But I know that the box at Forest at Medford Square, I think it's a mix of people who are ignorant that it's there.

948
01:19:13,989 --> 01:19:16,050
