959
01:19:44,611 --> 01:19:45,151
[SPEAKER_18]: Okay.

960
01:19:45,171 --> 01:19:47,571
[SPEAKER_18]: Each year we've been here, we add more and more.

961
01:19:47,611 --> 01:19:49,252
[SPEAKER_02]: So, so DBW reminds us that we're

962
