987
01:21:44,648 --> 01:21:56,899
[SPEAKER_03]: I would support that as long as you, I don't know how we designate, I don't want it to get lost in the other thousands of tabled items we have, but I don't know how we can designate that it's only tabled for a month to give the petitioner a chance to speak.

988
01:21:57,834 --> 01:22:20,990
[SPEAKER_05]: So, I mean, we've, we've done the timeframes in the past to some success, although you would not know it by looking at our table business but I will tell you that behind the scenes we are like my traffic division is working on these table items so that we can kind of start bringing them forward with some concrete factual information and start breaking them apart because I do not want to end up 2023 with two to three pages of table business so we can start clearing some of those out.

989
01:22:22,131 --> 01:22:28,321
[SPEAKER_05]: That gives me a chance to say that out loud, but I think at this point in time, this petitioner did state he was going to be here.

990
01:22:28,341 --> 01:22:34,391
